21:58.150 --> 21:59.118 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BORIS EPSHTEYN: Sure.

21:59.151 --> 22:00.119 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Sure.

22:00.152 --> 22:01.887 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Philip Gordon.

22:01.921 --> 22:03.389 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PHILIP GORDON: Well, we're
mostly talking
about foreign policy, but I
would come back,

22:03.422 --> 22:07.526 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Judy, to your question about Mr.
