his mouth,
Mr. Gordon.

22:35.988 --> 22:37.489 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And it's unfair to do so.

22:37.523 --> 22:39.291 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Hillary Clinton tried to worked
with Russia.

22:39.325 --> 22:40.292 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
She failed.

