26:18.610 --> 26:21.613 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Trump's business record offers
another look.

26:21.647 --> 26:23.415 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
William Brangham has that.

26:23.449 --> 26:27.486 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: To understand
Trump's vast
and varied business dealings,
we're joined

26:27.519 --> 26:31.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
