about his
career.

26:35.160 --> 26:40.165 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Marc Fisher is a senior editor
at The Washington
Post and co-author of the book
"Trump Revealed:

26:40.199 --> 26:43.936 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
An American Journey of Ambition,
Ego, Money
and Power."

26:43.969 --> 26:47.272 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And Tim O'Brien is executive
editor of Bloomberg
View.

26:47.306 --> 26:50.542 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
His book is called "Trump
nation: The Art
of Being the Donald."

26:50.576 --> 26:53.579 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Gentlemen, thank you both very
much for being
her.

26:53.612 --> 26:56.048 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Marc Fisher, I would like to
start with you.

26:56.081 --> 27:01.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Trump campaign is predicated
in large
part on the idea that Trump is a
magnificent

27:01.487 --> 27:05.090 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
