America back to
prosperity.

27:05.123 --> 27:08.760 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And you have done a long
analysis of what
his business career is like.

27:08.794 --> 27:11.163 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Is that a fair characterization
of him?

27:11.196 --> 27:12.831 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
