27:12.865 --> 27:15.067 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARC FISHER, The Washington
Post: Well, he's
certainly had a good deal of
success.

27:15.100 --> 27:17.402 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
