projects and he merely
rents out his name and gets a
guaranteed income

28:03.081 --> 28:04.516 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
stream from that.

28:04.550 --> 28:07.419 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Tim O'Brien, I
would put
this same question to thank.

28:07.452 --> 28:10.622 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I should say, for the
